{"id":5438,"date":"2016-05-02T00:02:17","date_gmt":"2016-05-02T00:02:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/?p=5438"},"modified":"2021-03-01T10:21:33","modified_gmt":"2021-03-01T15:21:33","slug":"5-yoga-tips-beginners-lose-weight-burn-fat-fast","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/5-yoga-tips-beginners-lose-weight-burn-fat-fast\/","title":{"rendered":"5 Yoga Tips for Beginners Losing Weight"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"701\" height=\"370\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/10\/shutterstock_207304351-e1459992294598.jpg\" alt=\"5 Yoga Tips for Beginners Losing Weight\" class=\"wp-image-1578\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/10\/shutterstock_207304351-e1459992294598.jpg 701w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/10\/shutterstock_207304351-e1459992294598-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/10\/shutterstock_207304351-e1459992294598-365x193.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 701px) 100vw, 701px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>1. Try not eating before you practice. &nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Performing yoga in a fasted state will make it more likely your body will pull its energy from your remaining fat stores and thus, will help you burn more fat.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>2. Don\u2019t skip relaxation. &nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The relaxation and meditation part of yoga helps to lower your cortisol levels. Cortisol is the stress hormone that has been shown to cause the gain and retention of stubborn body fat. Don\u2019t skip it!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">3. Certain poses will burn more fat. &nbsp;<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Some poses&nbsp;are good for digestion, other poses are good for strength, and some have more fat-burning potential. Focus in on the poses designed to help you burn more fat if weight loss is one of your goals!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>4. Breathe deeper through your routine. &nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>81% of fat cells actually leave the body through your breath, and breathing deeper will help you find greater relaxation in your muscles during poses.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>5. Don\u2019t underestimate the fat-burning potential of a calm yoga practice!&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A calm, consistent yoga practice has been proven in conclusive studies to help people burn more fat, control cravings, relieve stress, and can help totally transform the body. This isn\u2019t an opinion. These are the facts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>If you are looking for some additional tips and some actual poses to help you transform your body with yoga, our&nbsp;<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/yogafatlossbible.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Yoga Fat Loss Bible for Beginners<\/a><\/span>&nbsp;is a great place to start!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It comes with&nbsp;everything you need to get started, including&nbsp;a <strong>complete 6-week workout plan, a flexibility guide, and a beginner&#8217;s guide to meditation!<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/yogafatlossbible.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"600\" height=\"258\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\/Avocadu-Yoga-Fat-Loss-Bible.png\" alt=\"Avocadu Yoga Fat Loss Bible\" class=\"wp-image-26019\" title=\"Avocadu Yoga Fat Loss Bible\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/12\